net.java.jddac.common.util
Class GenericArgArrayStore

java.lang.Object
  net.java.jddac.common.util.GenericStore
      net.java.jddac.common.util.GenericArgArrayStore

public class GenericArgArrayStore
extends GenericStore

This class extends GenericStore with the addition of a property field for each record in the store. The property field is a nested ArgArray (or Vector). It is stored in the database in XML format. This class adds methods to set and get the ArgArray in object or string format.

The tables should be created with the following sql statements. These statements will need to be adjusted based on which database provider is used and if indexes are needed. 

   CREATE TABLE {basename} (id INTEGER AUTO_INCREMENT UNIQUE, name VARCHAR UNIQUE, pid INTEGER, argarray BLOB);
   CREATE TABLE {basename}_attr (id INTEGER, name VARCHAR, value VARCHAR);

See Also:
GenericStore, ArgArray
